Text: Oasis Rates Cc For the past two production months I have had rate issues with Oasis I just talked with Marilyn Gilliam and suggested that Natalie Baker be put on a distribution list so Natalie can work on the rates during the month instead of me coming down at the end of the month and needing rates fixed I was informed by Marilyn that we were not sending rates to Oasis and that we should be doing this which would help prevent rate discrepancies at the end of the month Mikeif you have any questions about sending the rates to Oasis you can contact Paul McPheeters at Oasis and he can assist you Nataliethis is just an FYI Stephen R Swisher Specialist Energy Operations Enron Net Works LLC Phone Fax Email
